title: 745. Thanksgiving Games Preview & Breaking Down College Job Openings
itunes:title: 745. Thanksgiving Games Preview & Breaking Down College Job Openings
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys break down various college football topics such as NIL deals and current big job openings. Then, the pair preview the Thanksgiving Day games.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
